org.eclipse.papyrus.RobotMLLibraries.RobotML_ModelLibrary.RobotML_DataTypes.sensor_datatypes

Interface DifferentialOdometry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DifferentialOdometryImpl

    public interface DifferentialOdometry
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Differential Odometry'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Header
    • Right distance
    • Left distance
    • Left velocity
    • Right velocity

    See Also:
    Sensor_datatypesPackage.getDifferentialOdometry()
